🗑️ How to Delete Your Account in Journai
To permanently delete your Journai account, follow these steps:

Open the app and go to your Home / JourneeBot screen.

Tap the profile icon in the top-right corner of the screen.

Scroll down and select “Settings.”

Scroll all the way to the bottom.

Tap “Delete Account.”

Confirm your choice when prompted.

⚠️ This action is permanent and cannot be undone.
